1. First we need to create a account. Let's go sign up one.

2. Fill in all the information we need. Don't worry about the username, we can change it anytime we want. 

3. Oh and you can't have the same account name with others.

4. Now we finished the sign up it's time to log in.

5. You can change your username, password and email in here. After you're finished remember to log out the system.
